OL,3,CBBC to air unseen series of MasterChef
OL,4,Cfeaturing Gregg Wallace and John Torode
OL,6,FThe latest amateur series of
OL,7,FMasterChef will air, the BBC has
OL,8,Fannounced.
OL,10,FThe unseen series was filmed before
OL,11,Fallegations against Gregg Wallace and
OL,12,FJohn Torode were upheld by an
OL,13,Findependent investigation.
OL,15,FA decision on airing the celebrity
OL,16,Fseries and Christmas special has not
OL,17,Fbeen decided, with plans to be
OL,18,Fconfirmed later in the year.
