OL,3,CBBC to air unseen series of MasterChef
OL,4,Cfeaturing Gregg Wallace and John Torode
OL,6,FThe BBC said it had come to the
OL,7,Fdecision after speaking with
OL,8,Fcontestants and that broadcasting the
OL,9,Fseries "in no way diminishes the
OL,10,Fseriousness" of the findings against
OL,11,FWallace or Torode.
OL,13,FA BBC spokesperson said: "After
OL,14,Fcareful consideration and consultation
OL,15,Fwith the contestants, we have decided
OL,16,Fto broadcast the amateur series of
OL,17,FMasterChef on BBC One and BBC iPlayer
OL,18,Ffrom 6 August."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
