OL,3,CBBC to air unseen series of MasterChef
OL,4,Cfeaturing Gregg Wallace and John Torode
OL,6,F"MasterChef is an amazing competition
OL,7,Fwhich is life-changing for the amateur
OL,8,Fchefs taking part. The focus of it has
OL,9,Falways been their skill and their
OL,10,Fjourney.
OL,12,F"This has not been an easy decision in
OL,13,Fthe circumstances and we appreciate
OL,14,Fnot everyone will agree with it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
