OL,3,CBBC to air unseen series of MasterChef
OL,4,Cfeaturing Gregg Wallace and John Torode
OL,6,F"In showing the series, which was
OL,7,Ffilmed last year, it in no way
OL,8,Fdiminishes our view of the seriousness
OL,9,Fof the upheld findings against both
OL,10,Fpresenters. We have been very clear on
OL,11,Fthe standards of behaviour that we
OL,12,Fexpect of those who work at the BBC or
OL,13,Fon shows made for the BBC.
OL,15,F"However, we believe that broadcasting
OL,16,Fthis series is the right thing to do
OL,17,Ffor these cooks who have given so much
OL,18,Fto the process. We want them to be
OL,19,Fproperly recognised and give the
OL,20,Faudience the choice to watch the
OL,21,Fseries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
