OL,3,CBBC to air unseen series of MasterChef
OL,4,Cfeaturing Gregg Wallace and John Torode
OL,6,F"At this stage we have not taken a
OL,7,Fdecision on the celebrity series and
OL,8,FChristmas special, which was filmed
OL,9,Fearlier this year, and we will confirm
OL,10,Four plans later in the year.
OL,12,F"Most importantly MasterChef is a
OL,13,Fbrilliant, much-loved programme which
OL,14,Fis bigger than any one individual.
OL,15,FThere are many talented, dedicated and
OL,16,Fhard-working people who make the show
OL,17,Fwhat it is. It will continue to
OL,18,Fflourish on the BBC and we look
OL,19,Fforward to it returning stronger than
OL,20,Fever in the future."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
