OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe statement followed news that John
OL,12,FTorode's contract on MasterChef would
OL,13,Fnot be renewed, as confirmed by the
OL,14,FBBC and production company Banijay UK.
OL,16,FTorode confirmed he was the subject of
OL,17,Fan allegation of using racist language
OL,18,Fthat was upheld as part of a review
OL,19,Fcarried out by law firm Lewis Silkin
OL,20,Finto the alleged behaviour of his co-
OL,21,Fpresenter Gregg Wallace.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
