OL,3,CBBC to air unseen series of MasterChef
OL,4,Cfeaturing Gregg Wallace and John Torode
OL,6,FTorode said he had "no recollection of
OL,7,Fthe incident" and was "shocked and
OL,8,Fsaddened" by the allegation.
OL,10,FIn November 2024, the show's
OL,11,Fproduction company, Banijay UK,
OL,12,Fannounced Wallace would step away from
OL,13,Fhis role on the BBC cooking show while
OL,14,Fhistorical allegations of misconduct
OL,15,Fwere investigated.
